# 🔎 COMMAND: search
Description: Searches the framework's internal database for exploits, payloads, recon modules, or targets. Matches keywords against path, name, CVE, category, or description.

Usage:
    search exploits [keyword] - Search exploit modules.
    search payloads [keyword] - Search available payload generators.
    search recon [keyword]    - Search reconnaissance and enumeration modules.
    search targets [keyword]  - Search the internal targets database.

Examples:
    search exploits dirtypipe
    search recon smb
    search targets 192.168.1.0/24